&reftitle.setup;
&reftitle.required;
This version uses the functions of the Enchant library by Dom Lachowicz. You need Enchant 1.2.4 or later. Enchant 2.0.0 or later is only supported as of PHP 8.0.0.
Enchant also requires Glib 2.6 or greater. Pre-compiled Windows libraries are available from &url.glib.windows;.
&reference.enchant.configure;
&reftitle.resources;
Prior to PHP 8.0.0, there are two types of resources in this extension. The first one is the broker (backends manager) and the second is for the dictionary.
